OL,3,CRoadworks to be lifted ahead of Easter
OL,4,Cgetaway
OL,6,FMore than 1,000 miles of roadworks in
OL,7,FEngland will be lifted to ease the
OL,8,FEaster getaway, the Department for
OL,9,FTransport has announced.
OL,11,FNational Highways will remove
OL,12,Froadworks from 1,127 miles of
OL,13,Fmotorways and major A roads by 6am on
OL,14,FThursday, meaning 97.5% of its network
OL,15,Fwill be free of traffic cones.
OL,17,FThey will not be reinstated until
OL,18,Fafter Easter Monday.
