OL,3,CRoadworks to be lifted ahead of Easter
OL,4,Cgetaway
OL,6,FMotorists are being advised to prepare
OL,7,Ffor congestion around town and city
OL,8,Fcentres, retail parks and major routes
OL,9,Fsuch as the M6 at Birmingham and
OL,10,Faround the Blackpool area, the south
OL,11,Fand western section of the M25 between
OL,12,Fthe M23 and M40, the M5 at Bristol and
OL,13,Fthe A303 in Wiltshire.
OL,15,FThe AA estimated that 19.1 million
OL,16,Fpeople in the UK will drive on Good
OL,17,FFriday, with 18.5 million hitting the
OL,18,Froad on Saturday and 18.2 million on
OL,19,Feach of Easter Sunday and Easter
OL,20,FMonday.
