OL,3,CRoadworks to be lifted ahead of Easter
OL,4,Cgetaway
OL,6,FThe RAC warned that drivers face a
OL,7,F"hat-trick of hold-ups" on Thursday,
OL,8,FGood Friday and Saturday as the bank
OL,9,Fholiday weekend coincides with the end
OL,10,Fof the Easter holidays for many
OL,11,Fschools.
OL,13,FTransport Secretary Heidi Alexander
OL,14,Fsaid: "Cutting journey times and
OL,15,Fsaving drivers money every year is all
OL,16,Fpart of our Plan for Change to raise
OL,17,Fliving standards and put more money in
OL,18,Fpeople's pockets.
