OL,4,Cgetaway
OL,6,F"We are tackling the real problems
OL,7,Fthat drivers face by lifting 1,127
OL,8,Fmiles of roadworks over Easter and
OL,9,Fcracking down on disruptive
OL,10,Fstreetworks to make journeys to see
OL,11,Floved ones as smooth as possible.
OL,13,F"This Government is also saving
OL,14,Fdrivers up to #500 a year, with
OL,15,Fcouncils soon to receive their record
OL,16,F#1.6 billion pothole funding and the
OL,17,Fcontinued freeze on fuel duty."
