OL,4,Cgetaway
OL,6,FThe RAC has previously said repair
OL,7,Fcosts can be up to #460 if a vehicle
OL,8,Fneeds to go to a garage after hitting
OL,9,Fa pothole.
OL,11,FThe Treasury has estimated that
OL,12,Ffreezing fuel duty and maintaining the
OL,13,F5p-per-litre cut will save the average
OL,14,Fcar driver #59 during this financial
OL,15,Fyear.
OL,17,FThe DfT announced in January it will
OL,18,Fdouble the level of fines for
OL,19,Fdisruptive streetworks by utility
OL,20,Fcompanies which overrun.
