OL,4,Cgetaway
OL,6,FIt will also require at least 50% of
OL,7,Fany revenue raised from lane rental
OL,8,Fcharges to be spent on highway
OL,9,Fmaintenance.
OL,11,FNational Highways director of
OL,12,Foperational services Andrew
OL,13,FButterfield said: "We expect the roads
OL,14,Fto be busy with people looking to make
OL,15,Fthe most of a long Easter weekend.
OL,17,F"That's why we are making journeys
OL,18,Feasier by removing a huge number of
OL,19,Froadworks.
