OL,6,F"Drivers should also take time to plan
OL,7,Fahead. Two of the top three causes of
OL,8,Fbreakdowns are tyre issues and empty
OL,9,Ffuel tanks.
OL,11,F"You can help prevent any breakdowns
OL,12,Fby following our advice: top up your
OL,13,Ffuel, oil and screenwash, plan your
OL,14,Fjourney, check your tyres and prepare
OL,15,Ffor all weather conditions."
